# FLOOR: the minimum supported OCP version for the RHCOS aliyun boot-image supply
# chain (P3-IMG.1). This file is committed, so the CI runner (which has NO local
# ansible/group_vars/all.yml) has an explicit, auditable floor decoupled from the
# operator's all.yml.
#
# This is NOT the list of versions to bake — that is derived at run time:
#   matrix (detect --all-from) = enumerate this minor .. the latest OCP release,
#   MINUS whatever bootimage/provenance/ already has (skip already-baked), and
#   optionally AND the AI-supported set (--ai-versions). GA-only by default.
# Single-version mode uses this line as the version to bake.
#
# detect reads the first non-comment, non-blank line below.
4.20.22
